Lyle Jeffs is the brother of polygamous sect leader Warren Jeffs . 
  Charlene Wall Jeffs says she was forced to leave the church last year for being 'unrighteous' She has been married to Lyle for 31 years and has 10 children with him . 
  She says the church has 'become even more disturbing than it was under Warren' She claims she was excommunicated in September 2014 and is fighting to have her two youngest children back . 
  Lyle is the leader of the Fundamentalist Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints . 
  He has multiple wives but Mrs Jeffs has been legally married to him since 1983 . 
  She has filed for divorce citing rape and illegal practices . 
 